# ============================================================================
# CA Certificate for test.mosquitto.org (port 8883 - MQTT over TLS 1.2/1.3)
#
# Obtain the current certificate with:
#   openssl s_client -connect test.mosquitto.org:8883 -showcerts </dev/null \
#     2>/dev/null | openssl x509 -outform PEM > mosquitto_ca.pem
#
# Or download from: https://test.mosquitto.org/ssl/mosquitto.org.crt
# Rename to mosquitto_ca.pem and place in this directory.
#
# For production use, replace with your broker's CA certificate.
# For Adafruit IO: use DigiCert Global Root CA
# For AWS IoT:     use Amazon Root CA 1 (AmazonRootCA1.pem)
# For HiveMQ Cloud: use their cluster CA cert
#
# PASTE YOUR CA CERTIFICATE BELOW (PEM format):
# ============================================================================
-----BEGIN CERTIFICATE-----
REPLACEME_PASTE_YOUR_CA_CERT_PEM_HERE
-----END CERTIFICATE-----
